list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Add TypeScript file and update workspace settings
Introduced a new `index.ts` file and updated `.idea/workspace.xml` to include recent template and exclude specific files. These changes enhance project organization and alignment with the IDE's auto-reload and file management features.

task.summary:
Add initial project setup with package.json and index.js
Set up a basic Node.js project with a package.json file and an index.js file. The package.json includes metadata and a placeholder test script, while index.js logs a simple welcome message.
